translation[10]{c,v,t}:
  21,1,"Chiŵandichile ku ŵandu chiŵalanjilo chao (chakwaŵalanga pa Kiyama), kutendaga ŵanganyao ali nkulilechelela ni kunyosya"
  21,2,"Ngachikwaichililaga chikumbusyo chilichose chasambano chakuumila kwa M’mbuje gwao, ikaŵeje kuti akasachipikanilaga aku alinkutenda chanache"
  21,3,"Mitima jao jichinyosyelaga, ni kusongonelanaga mwaasili aŵala ŵalitendele lupuso kuti: “Ana aju (Muhammadi ﷺ) ninduni, pangaŵaga mundu mpele jenumanja? Ana nkuuŵichilila usaŵi kutendaga jenumanja n’di nkulola?”"
  21,4,"Jwalakwe (Muhammadi ﷺ) jwatite: “Ambuje ŵangu akumanyilila liloŵe (lililyose lyalikuŵechetedwa) kumawunde ni petaka, soni Jwalakwe ni Jwakupikanichisya, Jwakumanyilila nnope.”"
  21,5,"Nambo ŵanganyao ŵatite: “(Ayi yaakuŵecheta Muhammadi ﷺ iŵele) sagamisi syewanganyichilane.” (Ndaŵi jine akutiji): “Nambo jute kuilukanya (nsyene).” (Pane ni akutiji): “Nambo jwalakweju nkwimba ilaanga, basi ayiche nacho kukwetu chisimosimo mpela yaŵatite pakutumisyilidwa (achimitume) ŵandanda.”"
  21,6,"Nganiukulupilileje paujo pao musi uliose m’misi jatwajijonasile (namuno kuti twajitumichisye isimosimo), ana ŵanganyao ni takulupilile"
  21,7,"Ni nganitutumisyeje paujo penu (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ) ikaŵeje ŵandu (ngaŵaga malaika) ŵatwaliji nkwajuwulila (maloŵe), basi mwawusyani achimisyene lukumbukumbu (lwaindu yakala), nam’baga jenumanja ngankumanyilila"
  21,8,"Soni nganitwatenda (achimitumeo) kuŵa ilu yangalya yakulya, nambo soni nganaŵa ŵandamo"
  21,9,"Kaneko twasimichisye chilanga chao (chakwakamuchisya kwa amagongo ŵao), basi ni twajokwele (achimitumeo) ni ŵatwasachile (mwa akwakuya ŵao), ni twajonasile ŵakupelenganya malile (pasambi)"
  21,10,"Chisimu pamasile patuntuluchisye ŵanganyammwe Chitabu (Qur’an), mwalakwemo mwana chikumbusyo chenu, ana ŵangali lunda"